Reaper - ()
- For every permanently dead player, the soul reaper will gain one soul. These souls can be used to trade for actions.
- 2 souls - Weak Protection for one player.
- 3 souls - Change faction (Assassin) kill into a strong attack for the night.
- 5 souls - Strong Protection on one player and strong Attack on one player.
- Each action has no cooldown, however only one action may be executed per night phase. Each action will only last for the night when used. Souls are gained immediately.
- Does not respawn.
